column5: I got the last container of crawlers at the Four Seasons 3 days ago.They won't be getting anymore in as the price got jacked up by the supplier.I went to Smitty's and they are out too. Leeches have been working as good as crawlers,some days better.Bill
Dutchie's in Perrault Falls had numerous dozens of crawlers in the cooler as of Friday so you can try there if you want to resupply.

Bill, Nice to see you at Gawleys last week. Thanks for the information on where to fish and what was working for you. Have a great remainder of your trip and keep us updated on how the fishing is. Mike
